description:
Nonaka Yuki is a member of the Hero Clan in Japan, a childhood friend of http://anidb.net/ch70590 [Toujou Basara] as well as the older sister of http://anidb.net/ch71452 [Nonaka Kurumi], making her the first child of Nonaka Kaoru and Shuuya. She is the initial observer watching over http://anidb.net/ch70589 [Naruse Mio] as such she attends the same school, as well as being the class representative of her class, where Mio and Basara are. She later becomes one of the main female protagonists of the series.
Source: Shinmai Maou no Keiyakusha Wiki
name: Nonaka Yuki
